title: Player Attack S03E24 720p HDTV h264-Berg
description:
Need for Speed has done away with the subtitles and the themes this time around, rebooting the series with a very impressive new racer. Jonny Robot chats to Ghost Games about what's in store.

We also sit down with Capcom to find out more about Street Fighter V - the long-promised beta test might have fallen over, but it looks like it should be worth the wait.

Looking back at last week's Gamescom, there was a bunch of cool stuff - if you missed it when it happened, we've got a quick recap just for you!

...plus, of course, we have all the latest gaming news as well - this is Player Attack
